2. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the capacity approaching iterative decoding thresholds, which is a topic related to computational complexity. 
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - LDPC codes are commonly used in communication systems, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper discusses the use of graph covers in LDPC code construction, which is a topic related to social and information networks. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the construction and properties of LDPC codes, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms.
